&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a dynamic, innovative and a passionate nurse? Do you strive for excellence and enjoying working in a dedicated caring team? Then North Devon District Hospital needs YOU!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for band 5 Nurses to join our team of Nurses on the gastroenterology and acute medicine ward. We would support your career development by opportunities to further your education in related subjects and specific training required for the knowledge and skills needed to be a Nurse on our ward. Newly qualified will be offered a preceptorship programme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;North Devon provides a lovely balance of a friendly hospital in an outstanding location between the moors and coast. This could be the perfect place for you to provide an excellent work/life balance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would love to hear from YOU!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For any further information, please contact Ward Manager Terri Blackburn on 01271 335914.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are a variety of posts available with full or part time hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;** As this post is in a shortage occupation code it qualifies for the Trust’s Recommend a Friend Scheme, please find further information on the attached link**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 22/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
